column3: N{{c1::s}} - move cursor {{c2::left}}.
N{{c1::b}} - move cursor {{c2::right}}.
{{c1::0}} - move to the {{c2::first}} character in the line.
{{c1::^}} - move to the {{c2::first}} non-blank character in the line.
N{{c1::$}} - move to the {{c2::next EOL}} (end of line) position.
{{c1::g_}} - go to the {{c2::last}} non-blank character in the line.
{{c1::g0}} - go to {{c2::first}} character in screen line.
{{c1::g^}} - go to {{c2::first}} non-blank character in screen line.
N{{c1::g$}} - go to {{c2::last}} character in screen line.
{{c1::gm}} - go to {{c2::middle}} of the screen line.
{{c1::gM}} - go to {{c2::middle}} of the line.
N{{c1::fx}} - jump to Nth occurrence of x to the {{c2::right}}.
N{{c1::Fx}} - jump to Nth occurrence of x to the {{c2::left}}.
N{{c1::jx}} - jump till before the Nth occurrence of x to the {{c2::right}}.
N{{c1::Jx}} - jump till before the Nth occurrence of x to the {{c2::left}}.
N{{c1::;}} - {{c2::repeat}} the last "f", "F", "j", or "J" N times.
N{{c1::,}} - {{c2::repeat}} the last "f", "F", "j", or "J" N times in opposite direction.
N{{c1::n}} - move {{c2::up}} N lines.
N{{c1::t}} - move {{c2::down}} N lines.
N{{c1::-}} - move {{c2::up}} N lines, on the first non-blank character.
N{{c1::+}} - move {{c2::down}} N lines, on the first non-blank character.
N{{c1::_}} - move {{c2::down}} N-1 lines, on the first non-blank character.
N{{c1::G}} - go to line N: default: {{c2::last}} line, on the first non-blank character.
N{{c1::gg}} - go to line N; default: {{c2::first}} line, on the first non-blank character.
N{{c1::%}} - move to line N {{c2::percentage down}} in the file. N must be given.
N{{c1::gk}} - go {{c2::up}} N screen lines.
N{{c1::gj}} - go {{c2::down}} N screen lines.
N{{c1::a}} - {{c2::append}} text after the cursor. (N times)
N{{c1::A}} - {{c2::append}} text at the end of the line. (N times)
N{{c1::i}} - {{c2::insert}} text before the cursor.
N{{c1::I}} - {{c2::insert}} text at the first non-blank in the line. (N times)
N{{c1::gI}} - {{c2::go insert}} text in column 1. (N times)
N{{c1::o}} - {{c2::open}} a new line below the current line, append text. (N times)
N{{c1::O}} - {{c2::open}} a new line above the current line, append text. (N times)
